{"tid":1610721,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（好撚重要）Tp-Link 又出事！ 黑客入侵控制","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T09:39:43.000Z","uid":55032,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a963268cd41ff9a1581a31e694bee0245ecb726a","tid":1610721,"uid":55032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:22:23.000Z","msg":"Tq link 旗下所有產品設計有漏洞 屋企個<br />\ncam 半夜三更自已郁 全屋訓哂 有黑客 <br />\n揼撚晒呢d垃圾產品 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTP-LINK 安全漏洞令全屋家電淪陷<br />\n<br />\n在沒有管理員憑證的命令中，存在一種與配置驗證類似的命令，可容許黑客傳送一個含有文件名稱、分號與參數的指令，從而啟動開採程序，更可與 SR20 建立連結，當黑客入侵之後便可設定最高權限，藉此執行任何命令。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 的資訊安全工程師 Matthew Garrett 指出，TP-Link 於 2016 年推出的家用 Router SR20 原來存有安全漏洞，如果受到黑客攻擊入侵的話，將會被執行任何命令，用家的私穩及重要資料或會受到不可預計的損失。"},{"pid":"1787acf8724a07af7406a25d762b64ea1ead0f8a","tid":1610721,"uid":55032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:23:49.000Z","msg":"連仔快高長大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6705ddd3045ec601ba20470865010fd682fcfa4d","tid":1610721,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:01:19.000Z","msg":"仆街 屋企全部router都tp link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連住覆緊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b797d2bdd06d5e9bf999986cc2cc3653d890155","tid":1610721,"uid":61084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:05:41.000Z","msg":"佢話Hacker係利用咗TP-Link Device Debug Protocol（TDDP）<br />\n刷翻個openwrt唔好比佢開debug protocol就應該解決到<br />\n好多大陸機都會留翻debug後門，就算software冇，hardware都會有<br />\n不過算數啦唉<br />\n一係netgear，一係linksys，平少少Asus+openwrt<br />\n用大陸礦難機自己睇住，stock firmware 九成裝咗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fb2bdc56eb5cb2892df8f8b932eb1f4dac0481","tid":1610721,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b797d2bdd06d5e9bf9999